title: News for the BBC's Doomsday Project and the future of the National Archive
itunes:title: News for the BBC's Doomsday Project and the future of the National Archive
itunes:subtitle: Michael Wood discusses the BBC’s Domesday Project, David Reynolds reflects on Operation Barbarossa, Angus Konstam considers the fate of Captain Kidd and the new CEO of the Nation Archives comments on the organisation’s future plans.
description:
